Design Notes

QUESTIONS:
- Can window resizing be prevented when the resize is not reasonable for the
  current layout?
- How can columns (and rows) be resized?  Is some sort of "fake window" needed
  to allow this?

DESIGN STAGES:
- Communicate with FVWM
- Create FVWM configuration variables specific to the module
- Keyboard navigation for unmanaged windows - using FVWM window switching rules
- Tiled Window Layout
- Keyboard navigation for managed windows
- Support window resizing
- Mouse navigation for managed windows
- Stacked Window Layout
- Full Screen Window Layout
- Multiple Desktops
- Multiple Columns
- Multiple Rows
- Multiple Monitors

